Package: ppd
Title: Posterior Predictive Reference Point Estimation
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Jim Ianelli [aut, cre]
Maintainer: Jim Ianelli <jim.ianelli@gmail.com>
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Jim", family = "Ianelli", email = "jim.ianelli@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Provides a starting point for posterior predictive reference
    point estimation workflows in fisheries applications. The initial package
    includes generic spawning potential ratio helpers and package infrastructure
    so age-structured model components can be added incrementally.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends:
    R (>= 4.1.0)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
